Trade/Device Name(s): FreeStyle Precision Pro Blood Glucose and β-Ketone Monitoring System
Regulation Name(s): Calculator/Data Processing Module for Clinical Use
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): FreeStyle Precision Pro Blood Glucose and β-Ketone Meter
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for the FreeStyle Precision Pro Blood Glucose and β-Ketone Monitoring System for quantitative measurement of glucose and β-ketone in whole blood samples.
Indications for Use Summary: For quantitative measurement of glucose and β-ketone in fresh capillary, venous, arterial, and neonatal whole blood as an aid to monitor diabetes control in professional healthcare settings; not for diabetes diagnosis or screening.
